<font size="2" face="Verdana, Arial">
The point of charisma is this.  It helps minorly, but the help increases based on the level difference of the mobs.  At level 60, you can only charm mobs 7 levels lower than you so its not of much value.  At level 60, your are also only mezzing blue mobs, so again: little effect.  At lower levels if you are charming high blues and mezzing white or higher con mobs, you will notice a more considerable effect with a higher charisma.  <P>Eventually, if you keep playing, everyone will be level 60.  Therefore think to the future and dont put starting points into charisma, and as you level up, start dropping the charisma gear for hps, ac, and resists.
